	  }, {
	    "name" : "Connection",
	    "values" : [ "keep-alive" ]
	  }, {
	    "name" : "Content-Length",
	    "values" : [ "0" ]
	  } ],
	  "keepAlive" : true,
	  "secure" : false
	}

 did not match expectation:

	{
	  "method" : "HEAD",
	  "path" : "/date"
	}

 because:

	method matches = true
	path matches = false
	query string parameters match = true
	body matches = true
	headers match = true
	cookies match = true
	keep-alive matches = true
	ssl matches = true
